---

<PageLayout title={HOME.TITLE} description={HOME.DESCRIPTION}>
  <Container>
    <h4 class="animate font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">
      Welcome to my corner of the internet
    </h4>
    <div class="space-y-16">
      <section>
        <article class="space-y-4">
          <p class="animate">
            I enjoy building things, so I thought
            it would be fun to make this website. Currently I work as a data scientist 
            (or ML engineer depending on some definitions), so I spend a lot of time 
            thinking about Machine Learning, data, statistics and software. I'm also a 
            doctor in Physics. That means I spent four years thinking about ethereal 
            concepts related to black holes and quantum mechanics, which are also very 
            cool subjects.
          </p>
          <p class="animate">
            Besides machine learning and physics, I'm trying to learn about other subjects 
            too. During my undergrad, I learned about the basics of electronics, but 
            never had the opportunity to anything useful with it. Recently, I've started 
            to tinker with it again, and it's a lot of fun.
          </p>
          <p class="animate">
            Another recent interest is economics. I've always regarded it almost as a 
            pseudo-science, and something quite boring to learn. I just imagine that 
            most economics were memorising initialisms and computing percentages. To be 
            fair, I think that was due to how it was taught at school. However, the 
            nature of my adult life and seeing the evolution of AI first hand have sparked
            my interest in it.
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="animate space-y-6">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-y-2 items-center justify-between">
          <h5 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">
            Latest posts
          </h5>
          <Link href="/blog">
            See all posts
          </Link>
        </div>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          {blog.map(post => (
            <li>
              <ArrowCard entry={post} />
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>

